Louisa Singleton and Ida Singleton, as Administratrices, etc., Appellants, v. State Savings Bank of Tallahassee, etc., Appellee. An Appeal from a Decree Of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Leon. TV. J. Oven-and S. H. Diamond, for Appellants; •

Appeal dismissed on praecipe of counsel for appellants.

No appearance for Appellee.
